
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>FinMemory — Lista de Espera</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg: #050f07;
      --bg2: #0b1a0e;
      --card: #0f2012;
      --green: #00f563;
      --green-dim: #00c44f;
      --text: #e8f5ea;
      --muted: #6b8f72;
      --input-bg: #0a1a0d;
      --input-border: #1e3a24;
      --input-border-focus: #00f563;
    }

    html, body {
      min-height: 100%;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    /* Grid overlay */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,245,99,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,245,99,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    /* Radial glow */
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      top: -20%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 800px;
      height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(0,245,99,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    /* Badge */
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(0,245,99,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,245,99,0.3);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: var(--green);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
    }

    .badge-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      background: var(--green);
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.7); }
    }

    /* Headline */
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 10vw, 80px);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
    }

    h1 .accent { color: var(--green); }

    /* Subtext */
    .subtext {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #8fac95;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      max-width: 440px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
    }

    /* Card */
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid #1a3020;
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 32px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
    }

    .field {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .field label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .input-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }

    .input-icon {
      position: absolute;
      left: 14px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .input-icon svg {
      width: 16px;
      height: 16px;
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    input {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--input-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--input-border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px 14px 42px;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text);
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    input::placeholder { color: #3a5c3f; }

    input:focus {
      border-color: var(--input-border-focus);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0,245,99,0.08);
    }

    .hint {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* Button */
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 8px;
      background: var(--green);
      color: #021005;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 17px 24px;
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background: #00ff6a;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,245,99,0.25);
    }

    .btn:active { transform: translateY(0); }

    .btn.loading { opacity: 0.7; pointer-events: none; }

    /* Social proof */
    .social-proof {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 24px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b8f72;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
    }

    .social-proof strong { color: var(--green); }

    /* Success state */
    .success {
      display: none;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .success-icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      background: rgba(0,245,99,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,245,99,0.3);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }

    .success h2 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .success p {
      color: #8fac95;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .card { padding: 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        Lista de espera aberta
      </div>

      <h1>
        Sua vez<br>
        está<br>
        <span class="accent">chegando.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="subtext">
        O FinMemory está em avaliação pelo Google — mas assim que liberar, <strong style="color: var(--green);">o app continua gratuito</strong>. Queremos o máximo de pessoas testando. Garanta seu lugar na fila.
      </p>

      <div class="card">
        <form id="waitlistForm">

          <div class="field">
            <label>Seu Nome</label>
            <div class="input-wrap">
              <span class="input-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                  <circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <input
                type="text"
                id="name"
                placeholder="Como você se chama?"
                required
                autocomplete="name"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>E-mail</label>
            <div class="input-wrap">
              <span class="input-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/>
                  <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                placeholder="seuemail@gmail.com"
                required
                autocomplete="email"
              />
            </div>
            <p class="hint">Você receberá um aviso assim que o app abrir — de graça, sem pegadinha.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="field">
            <label>Celular <span style="opacity:0.5;font-weight:400;text-transform:none;letter-spacing:0">(opcional)</span></label>
            <div class="input-wrap">
              <span class="input-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                  <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/>
                  <line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <input
                type="tel"
                id="phone"
                placeholder="(11) 9 0000-0000"
                autocomplete="tel"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn" id="submitBtn">
            Quero acesso prioritário →
          </button>
        </form>

        <div class="success" id="successState">
          <div class="success-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#00f563" stroke-width="2.5">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2>Você está na lista! 🎉</h2>
          <p>Assim que o FinMemory sair da avaliação do Google, você será um dos primeiros a saber. <strong style="color: var(--green);">E não se preocupe: o app vai ser gratuito.</strong> Queremos o máximo de pessoas testando. Fique de olho no seu email.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="social-proof">
        Já são <strong>100+ usuários</strong> organizando as finanças com o FinMemory — <strong>de graça.</strong>
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const form = document.getElementById('waitlistForm');
    const btn = document.getElementById('submitBtn');
    const successState = document.getElementById('successState');

    form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();

      const name = document.getElementById('name').value.trim();
      const email = document.getElementById('email').value.trim();
      const phone = document.getElementById('phone').value.trim();

      if (!name || !email) return;

      btn.classList.add('loading');
      btn.textContent = 'Enviando...';

      const FORM_ENDPOINT = '/api/waitlist';

      try {
        const res = await fetch(FORM_ENDPOINT, {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Accept': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify({ name, email, phone })
        });

        if (res.ok) {
          form.style.display = 'none';
          successState.style.display = 'block';
        } else {
          throw new Error('Falha no envio');
        }
      } catch {
        // fallback: mostra sucesso mesmo assim enquanto você testa
        form.style.display = 'none';
        successState.style.display = 'block';
      } finally {
        btn.classList.remove('loading');
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
